        public double getRank(java.lang.String name)
        Returns the rank in this game of the player with the given name. e.g. if a player with name DumbBot_1 finished in 5th place then calling getRank("DumbBot_1") will return 5. If DumbBot_1 and another player together finished in a shared 5 place, then calling getRank("DumbBot_1") will return 5.5.
